Invocation Name: leyton orient
des:
You can use the Leyton Orient app to ask about the latest Orient News and get information on upcoming matches, and more! 

After the Welcome Message, here are some things you can say:

- "Tell me about Orient News"
- "Match info"

Be sure to check back weekly for the latest updates!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
